Quickstash.com/
├── backend/
│   ├── routes/
│   ├── server.js
│   └── ...other backend files
├── frontend/
│   ├── public/
│   ├── src/
│   ├── build/              ← auto-generated after build
│   └── package.json        ← frontend-only package.json
├── .env                    ← contains MONGO_URI, STRIPE, etc.
├── package.json            ← root-level for Railway build/start
├── railway.json
└── netlify.toml            ← optional (safe to ignore if not using Netlify)
